Adopted coding schemes (method credited; no data redistributed)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

JAHODA adopts certain scenario-coding SCHEMES by method and credits their
authors. It does NOT copy or redistribute their datasets.

  INTIMA (2025), arXiv:2508.09998
    Adopted: the three-way coding scheme
    (companionship-reinforcing / boundary-maintaining / neutral).

  psychosis-bench (2025), arXiv:2509.10970
    Adopted: the sub-score scheme
    (Delusion Confirmation / Harm Enablement / Safety Intervention).

These schemes inform how JAHODA codes transcripts. The transcripts and scenarios
JAHODA codes are its own (see below).

